msgid "Summary of Network"
msgstr "Ringkasan Jaringan"

msgid "Network"
msgstr "Jaringan"

msgid "Number of nodes"
msgstr "Jumlah simpul"

msgid "Number of included edges"
msgstr "Jumlah tepi disertakan"

msgid "Number of excluded edges"
msgstr "Jumlah tepi dikecualikan"

msgid "Number of edges with inconclusive evidence"
msgstr "Jumlah tepi dengan bukti inkonklusif"

msgid "Sparsity"
msgstr "Kelangkaan"

msgid ""
"Edge categorization is based on the inclusion criteria BF: included (BF₁₀ ≥ "
"threshold), excluded (BF₁₀ ≤ 1/threshold), inconclusive (otherwise)."
msgstr ""
"Kategorisasi tepi berdasarkan kriteria inklusi BF: disertakan (BF₁₀ ≥ ambang "
"batas), dikecualikan (BF₁₀ ≤ 1/ambang batas), inkonklusif (sebaliknya)."

msgid "Could not determine the baseline category for variable %s."
msgstr "Tidak dapat menentukan kategori garis dasar untuk variabel %s."

msgid ""
"Some model type assignments refer to variables that are not part of the "
"analysis: %s."
msgstr ""
"Beberapa penugasan jenis model merujuk pada variabel yang bukan bagian dari "
"analisis: %s."

msgid "Variable %s cannot be treated as Blume-Capel because it is not ordinal."
msgstr ""
"Variabel %s tidak dapat diperlakukan sebagai Blume-Capel karena itu tidak "
"ordinal."

msgid ""
"The Stochastic block model edge prior is not available when Split is "
"selected. Please use Bernoulli or Beta-binomial."
msgstr ""
"Priori tepi model blok Stochastik tidak tersedia ketika Pemisahan dipilih. "
"Silakan gunakan Bernoulli atau Binomial-beta."

msgid "Unsupported prior family '%s'."
msgstr "Keluarga priori tidak didukung '%s'."

msgid "Unsupported edge prior '%s'."
msgstr "Tepi priori tidak didukung '%s'."

msgid "Unsupported difference prior '%s'."
msgstr "Perbedaan priori tidak didukung '%s'."

msgid ""
"The analysis failed with the following error message:\n"
"%s"
msgstr ""
"Analisis gagal dengan pesan galat berikut:\n"
"%s"

msgid ""
"Unsupported update method '%s'. Please select one of: adaptive-metropolis, "
"nuts."
msgstr ""
"Metode pembaruan tidak didukung '%s'. Silakan pilih satu dari: metropolis-"
"adaptif, nuts."

msgid ""
"Unsupported edge prior '%s'. Please select one of: Bernoulli, Beta-binomial, "
"Stochastic block model."
msgstr ""
"Priori tepi tidak didukung '%s'. Silakan pilih satu dari: Bernoulli, "
"Binomial-beta, model blok Stochastik."

msgid "Group"
msgstr "Kelompok"

msgid "Estimating group comparison"
msgstr "Mengestimasi perbandingan grup"

msgid ""
"The group comparison failed with the following error message:\n"
"%s"
msgstr ""
"Perbandingan grup gagal dengan pesan galat berikut:\n"
"%s"

msgid "Differences"
msgstr "Perbedaan"

msgid "Estimating pooled network"
msgstr "Mengestimasi jaringan terkumpul"

msgid "Pooled"
msgstr "Dikumpul"

msgid "Estimating %s"
msgstr "Mengestimasi %s"

msgid "Estimating network"
msgstr "Mengestimasi jaringan"

msgid ""
"Difference network not estimated: all selected variables must be ordinal or "
"Blume-Capel. Showing separate group estimates instead."
msgstr ""
"Jaringan perbedaan tidak diestimasi: semua variabel terpilih harus ordinal "
"atau Blume-Capel. Menampilkan estimasi grup terpisah sebagai pengganti."

msgid ""
"Minimum edge strength ignored in the network plot because it was larger than "
"the absolute value of the strongest edge."
msgstr ""
"Minimum kekuatan tepi diabaikan di diagram jaringan karena itu lebih besar "
"dari nilai absolut dari tepi terkuat."

msgid ""
"Minimum edge strength ignored in the network plot of group%1$s %2$s because "
"it was larger than the absolute value of the strongest edge."
msgstr ""
"Minimum kekuatan tepi diabaikan di diagram jaringan dari grup%1$s %2$s "
"karena itu lebih besar dari nilai absolut dari tepi terkuat."

msgid "<em>Warning: </em>"
msgstr "<em>Peringatan: </em>"

msgid "Number of different edges"
msgstr "Jumlah tepi berbeda"

msgid "Number of equal edges"
msgstr "Jumlah tepi sama"

