msgstr "Kedekatan"

msgid "Strength"
msgstr "Kekuatan"

msgid "Expected influence"
msgstr "Dampak terharapkan"

msgid "Centrality Plot"
msgstr "Diagram kepusatan"

msgid "Parameter HDI Plot"
msgstr "Diagram HDI Parameter"

msgid "Parameter HDI Plots"
msgstr "Diagram HDI Parameter"

msgid ""
"The difference parameter HDI plot shows the posterior mean and highest "
"density interval (HDI) for each pairwise difference in partial association "
"between groups. Positive values indicate a stronger association in the first "
"group; negative values indicate a stronger association in the second group."
msgstr ""
"Diagram HDI parameter perbedaan menampilkan rerata posterior dan interval "
"kepadatan tertinggi (HDI) untuk setiap perbedaan berpasangan di asosiasi "
"parsial antara grup. Nilai positif mengindikasikan asosiasi lebih kuat di "
"grup pertama; nilai negatif mengindikasikan asosiasi lebih kuat di grup "
"kedua."

msgid ""
"Posterior samples are required for the parameter HDI plot. Please ensure the "
"model was fitted with 'save = TRUE'."
msgstr ""
"Sampel posterior diperlukan untuk diagram HDI parameter. Silakan pastikan "
"model telah disesuaikan dengan 'save = TRUE'."

msgid "%d%% HDI of Partial Association"
msgstr "%d%% HDI dari Asosiasi Parsial"

msgid "Complexity plot"
msgstr "Diagram kompleksitas"

msgid "Complexity plots"
msgstr "Diagram kompleksitas"

msgid "Complexity Plot"
msgstr "Diagram Kompleksitas"

msgid "Posterior Probability"
msgstr "Probabilitas Posterior"

msgid "Number of edges"
msgstr "Jumlah tepi"

msgid "Structure Plot"
msgstr "Diagram Struktur"

msgid "Structure Plots"
msgstr "Diagram Struktur"

msgid "Edge Evidence Plot"
msgstr "Diagram Bukti Tepi"

msgid "Edge Evidence Plots"
msgstr "Diagram Bukti Tepi"

msgid "Edge evidence probability table"
msgstr "Tabel probabilitas bukti tepi"

msgid ""
"Bayes factors with values of infinity indicate that the estimated posterior "
"inclusion probability is either 1 or 0. Please see the help file for more "
"information."
msgstr ""
"Faktor bayes dengan nilai infinit mengindikasikan bahwa probabilitas inklusi "
"posterior terestimasi adalah baik 1 atau 0. Silakan lihat berkas bantuan "
"untuk informasi lebih lanjut."

msgid "Edge Specific Overview"
msgstr "Ikhtisar Spesifik Tepi"

msgid "difference"
msgstr "perbedaan"

msgid "equal"
msgstr "sama"

msgid "inconclusive"
msgstr "inkonklusif"

msgid "Relation"
msgstr "Relasi"

msgid "Difference Estimate"
msgstr "Estimasi Perbedaan"

msgid "Posterior Diff. Prob."
msgstr "Prob. Perb. Posterior"

